The Herald Nyore Madzianike Senior Court Reporter Goodness and Mercy Ministries leader Prophet Tapiwa Freddy was today cleared of the rape and physical abuse charges he was facing at the Harare Magistrates Court. Harare regional magistrate Mrs Gloria Takundwa discharged Freddy after noting that the truth was not told in the whole matter. Mrs Takundwa said the State had failed to prove a prima facie against the clergyman.